pipeline_summary.name: check_pcd_sftp_folder_pipeline
pipeline_summary.description: Staged ETL pipeline for Primary Care Data processing

components.name: Check PCD SFTP Folder
components.description: Verifies the availability and contents of the SFTP folder before the ETL pipeline starts.

components.name: Check PCD Shared Folder
components.description: Validates accessibility of the shared folder after the SFTP check.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful SFTP folder check.

components.name: Extract PCD API Data
components.description: Sends POST requests to multiple PCDrelated HTTP endpoints in parallel and validates that each response returns status code 200.

upstream_policy.description: Triggered after shared folder validation completes.

components.name: Process and Upload PCD Data
components.description: Runs a Kubernetes job that processes all extracted API data and uploads the resulting PCD dataset to the target storage.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after all API extraction tasks have completed successfully.

components.name: Send ETL Notification Email
components.description: Sends an email summarizing the ETL run, indicating success or failure and listing any failed tasks.

upstream_policy.description: Executes regardless of success or failure of upstream tasks.
